text: Eastern Kentucky University is a university in Kentucky in the United States. Eastern Kentucky's athletics teams are called the Colonels and they have 15 varsity teams and have a rivalry with Western Kentucky University. The president of Eastern Kentucky is Dr. Charles Doug Whitlock. ==References== == Other websites == * Eastern Kentucky University Official website Category:Colleges and universities in Kentucky Category:Ohio Valley Conference Category:1906 establishments in the United States Category:20th-century establishments in Kentucky
